    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "thinking",
      "content": "你刚才说王有个超酷的绝招？是什么呀？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "surprised",
      "content": "那就是王车易位！这是国际象棋里唯一一步能同时走两个棋子的特殊走法！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "surprised",
